"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-2155467-olympic-sport-struck-penis-gate-chaos\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  In an Olympic sport determined by distance, some athletes are reportedly going to extraordinary lengths to gain an extra few inches - and that's before they have even launched themselves off the ramp.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With just weeks remaining until the Winter Olympics in Italy, ski-jumping has been engulfed by 'penis-gate', with athletes allegedly believing bigger is better by injecting their private parts, according to German outletBild.\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 258, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.6204386845471903, \"rank\": 0.6114407550415332, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 410, \"end\": 416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.5921232033482268, \"rank\": 0.6886660490121207, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The report suggests 3D scanner measurements for the crotch region of their jumpsuits are taken from the lowest point of the athlete's manhood - meaning any additional growth could provide a competitive edge before they even take flight.\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Consequently, when launching, the surface area of the athlete becomes considerably larger, which enhances the likelihood of a superior jump.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's this revelation that has reportedly prompted some athletes to inject hyaluronic acid into a silicone condom-like apparatus worn beneath their trousers.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 968, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Halvor Egner Granerud, a Norwegian ski jumper, was incensed by the allegations when approached by Dagbladet.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 979, \"end\": 1000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Halvor_Egner_Granerud\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Halvor Egner Granerud\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4270517\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Halvor_Egner_Granerud\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Halvor_Egner_Granerud\"}, {\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9999689853180614, \"rank\": 3.0952926624854895e-05, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dagbladet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dagbladet\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dagbladet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dagbladet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Rune Velta [Norwegian coach] came into the locker room before the qualifiers and said: 'You have to be prepared for questions about penis injections'.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9999689853180614, \"rank\": 3.0952926624854895e-05, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have to admit that I thought it was nonsense.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No, I have never heard of it until today.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When I took my measurements, it was with a doctor who examined me to make sure I did not have a fake penis.\\\"\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued: \\\"I assume they are speculating about something like the body scan before the season.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's true: It's better to be warm and comfortable than a little cold when measuring.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That could be true, he says.\\\"\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1882, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Norwegian officials have previously acknowledged tampering with competition suits during a World Cup event in Trondheim last year, where they incorporated reinforced threading into the garments designed to enhance aerial performance.\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2017, \"end\": 2026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trondheim\", \"score\": 0.9999999975279934, \"rank\": 1.4965001196791642e-09, \"text\": \"Trondheim\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trondheim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trondheim\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jan-Erik Aalbu, the federation's general manager, was forthright in his assessment: \\\"The way I consider this...we have cheated,\\\" adding: \\\"We have tried to cheat the system.\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That is unacceptable.\\\"\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH